<plot>Donald (30) is Britain's only remaining professional Knight in shining Armour. From the bedroom of his parents house, in the heart of Devon, he provides a 24 hour emergency call out service to anybody in distress This bitter-sweet 'Mockumentary' explores the issues of where the boundaries of determination and delusion lie, but also poses the question of what is wrong with a little delusion if it's all that gets you out of bed in the morning.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?011362</url></doc>
